# 个人本地配置（敏感）
**/.claude/settings.local.json
**/.claude/.env
**/.claude/.env.*
**/.claude/*.key
**/.claude/*.pem
**/.claude/secrets/

# 缓存和日志
**/.claude/cache/
**/.claude/logs/
**/.claude/tmp/
**/.claude/*.log

# 备份文件
**/.claude/*.bak
**/.claude/*.backup
**/.claude/.DS_Store

# 本地历史（如有）
**/.claude/.history
**/.claude/.claude-history